where in order to get Eq.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:specificrecursion"

\end_inset

 we have used Eq.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:DeductionRelation"

\end_inset

.
 With these simplifications, we plug Eq.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:basisBessel-1"

\end_inset

 into Eq.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:bdg1-1-1-1"

\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:bdg2"

\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
