\left(k_{z}^{2}+\frac{q^{2}}{4}+k_{z}q+\lambda(k_{z}+\frac{q}{2})+h+a^{2}\right)\frac{1}{A}J_{0}(ar)u-i\lambda b\frac{1}{B}J_{0}(br)\alpha-\Delta\frac{1}{A}J_{0}(ar)v & = & E\frac{1}{A}J_{0}(ar)u\label{eq:bdg1-1}\\
i\lambda ae^{i\theta}\frac{1}{A}J_{1}(ar)u+\left(k_{z}^{2}+\frac{q^{2}}{4}+k_{z}q-\lambda(k_{z}+\frac{q}{2})-h+b^{2}\right)\frac{e^{i\theta}}{B}J_{1}(br)\alpha+\Delta\frac{e^{i\theta}}{B}J_{1}(br)\beta & = & E\frac{e^{i\theta}}{B}J_{1}(br)\alpha\label{eq:bdg1-2}\\
