\end_inset

We multiply both sides of Eq.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:bdg1-1"

\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:bdg1-4"

\end_inset

 by 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{0}^{1}\frac{1}{A}J_{0}(ar)rdr$
\end_inset

 and Eq.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
